### 5. MODULE AND PROMPT ECOSYSTEM

**a. Core System**
WikidAI Core (backend orchestration, prompt logic, UI educational features) may not be redistributed or sold. Use in other AI orchestration products requires explicit licensing.

**b. Community Modules**
Third-party agents or extensions authored independently may be licensed under any open license chosen by their creators, provided attribution and compatibility with WDL terms.

**c. Prompt and Knowledge Assets**
All provided prompts (system instructions, SPARQL examples, workflow patterns) are integral to the educational purpose of WikidAI and remain under copyright. Adaptation is permitted for research, but public redistribution of modified prompt sets requires approval.

